description.text:
This model was printed twice and stuck together. Used 2 separate PLA filaments (red &amp; black) using the Replicator 2 on medium settings. Could use a bit of sanding on the top and sides. Prints out to about: 4&quot;x 3.5&quot;  
For info on the University visit: <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.wisc.edu" >http://www.wisc.edu</a>   
Enjoy!
